1949;;The Huggetts Abroad;;British;;Ken Annakin;;Jack Warner, Kathleen Harrison, Dinah Sheridan, Jimmy Hanley;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Huggetts_Abroad;;After Joe Huggett loses his job, the family decide to emigrate to South Africa, travelling via a land route that takes them across Africa. On their journey they become entangled with a diamond smuggler.